Package: phyland
Type: Package
Title: Simple and fast phylogeographic analysis in R using structured coalescent models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-09-06
Author: Erik Volz and Simon Frost
Maintainer: Erik Volz <erik.volz@gmail.com>
Description: This package extends the phydynR package to implement classic 'island' models for migration of lineages between discrete demes. Typical usage would involve using a dated tree and location of sampling for each lineage to infer migration rates between different spatial locations. 
Depends: phydynR,bbmle
License: MIT
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
